reviews.text: Portions were very small for the price, but it was delicious. The noodles were really thin and could be finished in a few bites. The soup was so rich in flavor.

The portion was small and it was too salty for me but I don't cook with salt. So for others it might be balanced. Taste was good though. Tried the shrimp with fried noodles.
The service is very friendly that's why it's a 3 and not lower.

One of The most delicious chinese noodles I've tasted. Staff are helpful and nice even if they have a hard time speaking English.  
More power!
Noodles texture was alright, quite pricey for a small bowl of noodle.
I think the taste was very good and price was decent. I highly recommend the beef brisket with wonton noodle soup!

result.name: 麥奀雲吞麵世家

html_attributions: หารชัย สังวรกิจธรรม

reviews.text:
基本的に麺です。器は小さ目でちょうど良い。
もちろん味も良い。海老ワンタン麺はメニューの一番最初に書いてあるヤツです。メニューから選ぶときは文字で判断するけど、分からない人は壁に貼ってるおススメの品の写真を指差してもいいと思う。麺は小ぶりなので、しっかりとした食事をするのなら、小皿料理も頼んだ方が良いと思います。
Portions were very small for the price, but it was delicious. The noodles were really thin and could be finished in a few bites. The soup was so rich in flavor.

海老ワンタン麺🍜🍥が43H$です。
容器が小さいのに驚く👀‼️かもしれませんが、麺は細く、スープは絶品です‼️
お茶🍵が出るのが珍しいです。
チェーン店なので、いろんな場所に有ります‼️
深い緑色の店舗が目印です。
是非‼️お立ち寄り下さい❗️
在isquare旁邊位置十分方便，裝修別緻。 平日晚上的時候也不算多人。
就是好吃，但是十年來似乎不斷漲價。
